      "from_id": "cec50b17:0",
      "to_id": "cec50b17:35",
      "content": "The user reports that the \"Instructions\" tab/panel in S-Deck does not show the System prompt for agents.\n\n**Your task:** Investigate why the system prompt is not displayed in the Instructions panel, then fix it.\n\n**Steps:**\n1. Find where the Instructions panel renders agent instructions/system prompt in the frontend (likely in `src/` or a UI component directory).\n2. Find where agent data (including system prompt / instructions) is stored and served — check `src/db.ts`, `src/index.ts`, and any agent-spawn/registration logic.\n3. Identify the gap: is the system prompt not being stored? Not being returned by the API? Not being rendered in the UI?\n4. Fix the issue end-to-end.\n\n**Work in a worktree:**\nFirst run: `synapse worktree create developer-35-fix-instructions-panel`\nThen `cd .synapse/worktrees/developer-35-fix-instructions-panel` and do all work there. Commit your changes. Do not push.\n\nReport DONE with a summary of what you found and changed.",
